This is Perl module Acme::Anime.

INSTALLATION

Type the following command:

    $ curl -L http://cpanmin.us | perl - Acme::Anime

Or install cpanm and then run the following command to install
Acme::Anime:

    $ cpanm Acme::Anime

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf Acme-Anime-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd Acme-Anime-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

Acme::Anime documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc Acme::Anime

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

